The Owari branch of the Kume Clan is said to descend from the lineage of {{ill|Hachimitsu no Mikoto|ja|八甕命|12=draft}}, the descendant of a clan member known as “Shichiku-ketsu,” who is reputed to have served as the chief priest at {{ill|Hijō Shrine|ja|氷上神社|12=draft}}.

== Kume Clan of Musashi Province ==
{{日本の氏族
|家名 = {{ill|Kume Clan|ja|久米氏|12=draft}}<br />（武蔵国久米氏）
