|本貫 = [[Yamato Province]] [[Takaichi District]] Kume-gō
|人物 =
|後裔 =
}}
The branch known as Kume Omi (久米臣) originated from the Kume-gō of [[Yamato Province]] [[Takaichi District]] and is considered a branch of the Kasuga clan’s Wagetsu lineage.

== Kume Clan of Owari Province ==
{{日本の氏族 (古代氏族)
