The Musashi branch of the Kume Clan originated from Kume-shō in [[Musashi Province]] [[Iruma District]] and is considered a branch of the Murayama line, which claims descent from the Kanmu Heishi.

== Kume Clan of Hitachi Province ==
{{日本の氏族
|家名 = {{ill|Kume Clan|ja|久米氏|qq=draft}}<br />（常陸国久米氏）
|家紋 =
