== Kume Clan of Hitachi Province ==
{{日本の氏族
|家名 = {{ill|Kume Clan|ja|久米氏|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kume Clan|qq=}}<br />（常陸国久米氏）
|家紋 =
|家紋名称 =
|本姓 = 1. {{ill|Fujiwara Northern Family|ja|藤原北家|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara Northern Family|qq=}} (Hidesato lineage, also associated with the Onozaki clan)<br />2. {{ill|Seiwa Genji|ja|清和源氏|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seiwa Genji|qq=}} (Yoritomo lineage, with a branch related to the Satake clan)
|家祖 = {{ill|Satake Yoshitake|ja|佐竹義武|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Satake Yoshitake|qq=}} (Kume Yoshitake)
|種別 = {{ill|Buke|ja|武家|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Buke|qq=}}
|出身地 = [[Hitachi Province]] [[Kuzugun]] Kume-gō
|根拠地 = Hitachi Province, Kuzugun, Kume-gō
|人物 =
|支流 =
